Package de.ryanthara.ja.rycon.tools

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileToolsExcel
    FileToolsExcel implements basic file operations to write Microsoft xls, xlsx, ... files.
    FileToolsLeicaGSI
    This class implements several basic operations on Leica GSI files.
    FileToolsODF
    FileToolsODF implements basic file operations to write Open Document Format spreadsheet files.
    FileToolsText
    This class implements basic operations on text based measurement and coordinate files.
    ImageConverter
    ImageConverter converts images between AWT, Swing and SWT with support for Apple retina displays.
    NumberHelper
    NumberHelper implements basic helper operations for numbers.
    SimpleChecker
    SimpleChecker provides a set of simple check routines in RyCON.
    Updater
    Updater holds all the update functionality for RyCON.
